    public class Tk_GraphLegend
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Create a legend for a task history graph. The legend is a JPanel that contains other JPanels for the legend entries.
    Author:
    michaelwebster

    • Constructor Detail

      • Tk_GraphLegend

        public Tk_GraphLegend(java.awt.Rectangle r)

        Create the Tk_GraphLegend with the given size. The legend is created by:

        1. Obtain the static texture map from the Tk_BarChartEntry class.
        2. Create the legend's JPanels and store them in the private vector m_legendEntrys
        3. Add all the JPanels in m_legendEntry to this class's panel.

        Parameters:
        r - The rectangular bounds for this JPanel container.

    • Method Detail

      • createLegendEntries

        private void createLegendEntries()
        Create texture label and task name JLabels for the legend entries. Add the task name string to the task name panel, and paint a square sample of the texture paint corresponding to that task name into the texture label. Add the texture label an task name label to a new JPanel, and add that JPanel to the m_legendEntries Vector.
